title: HYDRATION NATION: CORONA DEL MAR HIGH SCHOOL
description: On World Water Day 2013 we brought Rob Machado and Hurley H2O to one of the local high schools to kick off their involvement in our latest program: Hydration Nation. To see how your high school can be involved, please visit http://hurley.com/hydrationnation
